@host = https://localhost:7022

### Resolve a slug (replace abc1234 with a real slug from the API create response)
# Send an iOS User-Agent to exercise a Device=Ios rule.
GET {{host}}/abc1234
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (iPhone; CPU iPhone OS 17_0 like Mac OS X) AppleWebKit/605.1.15

### Resolve as Android
GET {{host}}/abc1234
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 14; Pixel 8) AppleWebKit/537.36

### Health
GET {{host}}/health
